Text: Houston GBN Steering Committee June this just a reminder that we have a meeting of the steering committee of the Houston chapter of the GBN this Sunday at at Guadalajara Attached is a proposed agenda Please let myself or Glenn know if you will there Thanks Chris GBN Agenda doc
GBN Sunday Meeting Agendais an agenda for this Sundays meeting of the Houston steering committee of the UT GBN I will see you there CJ GBN Agenda doc

March th Mtg WriteUpof Events for Houston chapter March th Steve Patterson Houston NFL Holdings March st Houston Aeros Game with Texas Exes May th Deed Vest Rockwell International May th or July nd Houston Astros game with Texas Exes September th Panel on Houstons Economy in the new millenium confirmed speakers are Harvey Bunce UT Galveston Medical Center Shirley Delibero Metro Robert Duncan Transwestern Real Estate and Paul Murphy Southwest Bank of Texas Issues to be addressed with those events Sponsor needed for May th event We will discuss with Deed Vest at this Wednesdays event Need speaker from energy and from high tech for September event Will ask Mike Hansen to contact Ashfordcom people to seek interest from high tech Need UT professor to act as moderator of event Will talk to Arrion this Wednesday about this Need more sponsors for September event Carolyn will give me Robert Duncans number and Melinda Perrins number for contact Want to involve TBN in September event Glenn will contact local chapter leader Need date for baseball game Chrissy will stay on top of this New Items Glenn and Chrissy are working on family oriented activity for JuneAugust We need another event in October to early November time frame possibly another speaker event Next Meeting April th at Guadalajara at See you Wednesday night Chris

Houston GBN Steering Committee Sunday March this a reminder that we have a Houston GBN steering committee meeting this Sunday March th at pm at Guadalajara Restaurant on between Buffalo Speedway and Kirby Please let myself of Glenn know if you can make it Hopefully you have received invites or emails about the Steve Patterson event on March th and the Houston Aeros game with the Texas Exes on March st Chris
